{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block content %}
    <section>
        <h2>phpbotgram documentation</h2>

        <p>
            phpbotgram is a modern PHP 8.5 port of aiogram for Telegram bots.
            It keeps the familiar Bot, Dispatcher, Router, filters, middlewares,
            FSM, and scenes model, but runs on amphp fibers and uses PHP-native
            types throughout.
        </p>

        <h3>Start with the guide</h3>
        <p>
            The narrative documentation is the best entry point for building a
            bot, finding task-oriented recipes, and understanding the framework
            pieces before jumping into generated symbols.
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="guide/index.html">Guide overview</a></li>
            <li><a href="guide/tutorial/index.html">Getting started tutorial</a></li>
            <li><a href="guide/how-to/index.html">How-to recipes</a></li>
            <li><a href="guide/concepts/index.html">Concepts</a></li>
        </ul>

